OL,3,CFour further arrests made in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FFour more people have been arrested
OL,7,Fafter a father-of-three was stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath.
OL,10,FThe man in his 30s, who has been named
OL,11,Flocally as Adrian Brown, died in
OL,12,Fhospital after he was attacked on Raby
OL,13,FStreet, in Moss Side, Manchester, at
OL,14,Faround 11pm on Friday 8 May.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed
OL,17,Fthat a 24-year-old man has been
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of murder, and
OL,19,Ftwo men - aged 25 and 38 - and a 26-
OL,20,Fyear-old woman have been arrested on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
