OL,3,CFour further arrests made in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FThese arrests bring the total number
OL,7,Fof people in custody to five. An 18-
OL,8,Fyear-old man was previously arrested
OL,9,Fon suspicion of murder on Saturday, 9
OL,10,FMay, and remains in police custody.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,13,FEdwards described the updates as a
OL,14,F"significant step" to "securing
OL,15,Fjustice for the victim and his family."
OL,17,F"We now have five people in custody
OL,18,Ffollowing this tragic incident," DCI
OL,19,FEdwards said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
